name: Transcicada
desc: If this card is Special Summoned: You can Special Summon 1 "Husk Token" (Insect/EARTH/Level 3/ATK 0/DEF 0), also while that Token is in a Monster Zone, you cannot Special Summon monsters from the Extra Deck, except Insect monsters. You can only use this effect of "Transcicada" once per turn.
